# My Personal Website

## Description
This is my personal website project, built to showcase my portfolio, blog, and contact information. It's a simple, responsive site designed with modern web technologies.

## Features
- Responsive design for mobile and desktop
- Portfolio section with project highlights
- Blog with markdown support
- Contact form

## Technologies Used
- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript
- [Framework/Libraries, e.g., React, if applicable]

## Installation
1. Clone the repository: `git clone https://github.com/yourusername/my-personal-website.git`
2. Navigate to the project directory: `cd my-personal-website`
3. Install dependencies: `npm install` (if using Node.js)
4. Run the development server: `npm start`

## Usage
- Open `index.html` in your browser for a static site.
- For dynamic features, follow the installation steps above.

